    question: 'Shopify Email or Drip for cart recovery?',
    answer: 'Choose Shopify Email when Shops wanting low-friction email inside Shopify Admin. Choose Drip when Teams wanting visual workflows and behavior-based segmentation. Sequenzy still leads as lifecycle layer if neither owns strategy.',
